{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/bandung-hallowland-talkshow-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Komik Lieur Ungkap Style Kumaha Urang-nya di Bandung Hallowland","content":"<p>Semakin hari, semakin banyak komik Indonesia yang terbit setiap harinya. Mau nggak mau, para <em>author</em> harus bersaing untuk menyajikan cerita yang menarik dan gambar yang memukau. Agar bisa selangkah lebih maju, para <em>author</em> harus memiliki <em>style</em> yang unik dari segi narasi dan visual. Namun, bagaimana caranya untuk menemukan <em>style</em> unik yang beda dari orang lain?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51639\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51639\" data-attachment-id=\"51639\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bandung-hallowland-talkshow-komik/attachment/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51639\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" alt=\"bandung hallowland\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/01-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51639\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Untuk menjawab pertanyaan tersebut, empat komikus membuka rahasia komik mereka di <em>talkshow</em> “Karya Urang Kumaha Urang.” <em>Talkshow</em> yang diadakan di acara Bandung Hallowland ini menampilkan empat komikus populer. Mereka adalah <em>author</em> Komik Lieur <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/sagus-komik-lieur-terinspirasi-dari-pengalaman-saya-waktu-kecil/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sagus</a>, <em>author</em> GHOSTY’s Comic <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/know-your-judges-1-fajar-ghosty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fajar Ghosty</a>, <em>author</em> Risa Comics Excel Coananda, dan <em>author</em> Infernum dan dosen DKV Unikom Camsterkicks.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51640\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51640\" data-attachment-id=\"51640\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bandung-hallowland-talkshow-komik/attachment/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51640\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/02-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51640\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Sepanjang sesi <em>talkshow</em> pada tanggal 4 November 2018 lalu di teater tertutup Dago Tea House Bandung, keempat narasumber membeberkan cerita bagaimana mereka mulai berkiprah di dunia komik. Sagus misalnya, dimana ia termotivasi untuk menggambar dengan lebih serius dan niat agar bisa dipuji gurunya. Lain lagi dengan Fajar, yang menjaga <em>style</em> karakternya sejak masih menggambar di kertas binder sewaktu masih SMP.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bercanda-bareng-somad-dan-teman-teman-di-komik-lieur/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bercanda Bareng Somad dan Teman-Teman di Komik Lieur</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51641\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51641\" data-attachment-id=\"51641\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bandung-hallowland-talkshow-komik/attachment/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51641\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51641\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Para <em>author</em> pun memberikan tips dan trik untuk bisa mengekspresikan diri dengan bebas menggunakan media komik. Salah satu caranya adalah percaya diri dengan kemampuan yang ada dan memaksimalkan yang saat ini sudah dimiliki. Salah satu contohnya adalah Fajar dan Excel, yang meskipun kemampuan ilustrasi mereka terbatas, namun bisa menciptakan narasi yang <em>engage</em> dengan para pembacanya. Saat ini, komik mereka telah dibaca puluhan ribu <em>followers</em> setiap harinya.</p>\n<p>Para <em>author</em> juga membagikan tips dan trik untuk menggaet pembaca. Karena semua <em>author</em> besar dari sosial media, mereka semua memberikan kiat-kiat memaksimalkan jangkauan pembaca di Facebook hingga Instagram.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lingkarya-moesia-author-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Lingkarya Moesia dan Author CIAYO Comics Hadir di Bandung</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51642\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51642\" data-attachment-id=\"51642\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bandung-hallowland-talkshow-komik/attachment/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51642\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/04-bandung-hallowland-talkshow-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51642\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Apa kamu sempat menonton <em>talkshow</em> mereka di event Bandung Hallowland? Mana <em>author</em> komik yang membuatmu paling terkesan? Jangan lupa kalau CIAYO Comics juga punya berbagai komik dengan <em>style</em> unik, yang bisa kamu baca dengan mengklik gambar di bawah.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/comedy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50178\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komik-ms-paint-bikin-netizen-ketawa/attachment/print-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534763793&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Komik Komedi CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50178\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy.jpg\" alt=\"Banner Komik Komedi\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Comedy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"p